18.	Other Information
If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, or you want to object to or restrict any processing of your information, please contact us regarding this policy at
privacy-weg@wacom.com
.
You have the right to reach out and communicate with a supervisory authority (i.e., an independent public authority which is established by an EU Member State) to lodge a complaint, but we would appreciate the opportunity to speak with you first and resolve your issues.
