1.	Our Contact Details
This privacy policy is issued on behalf of Wacom EuropeGmbH, Zollhof 11-15, 40221 Düsseldorf, Germany.
If you have any questions, comments, or concerns about this policy or our use of your personal information, you may contact us at
privacy-weg@wacom.com
.
